| pure_algebraic | 137 | 4.3e-06 | 1e-3 | ✓ |
| SR | 136 (+1 boundary) | 1.7e-06 | 1e-3 | ✓ |
| Schwarzschild | 137 | 4.4e-04 | 1e-3 | ✓ |

One SR row (`t = 0.9999`, `w ≈ 2.0e-4`) is **declared unresolved** by the FD-operand-variation
